value: Probably breeds in eastern Siberia ^ (no actual breeding localities known). Winters in the Philippines, Caroline Islands, Malay Archipelago and Celebes to New Guinea and Australia; on migration through Trans- baikalia, Sakhalin and the Kurile Islands, the Japanese islands, Formosa and eastern China.
